OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis clearly would mean keeping a large
OL,7,Feditorial operation in Aberdeen and the
OL,8,Fnorth of Scotland.
OL,10,FStudio presentation and production can
OL,11,Fmove to Glasgow without Ofcom
OL,12,Fpermission.
OL,14,FRealistically, if any dedicated output
OL,15,Ffor the north remained it would have to
OL,16,Fbe recorded.
