OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FMy own suspicion is that Ofcom will
OL,7,Feither approve STV's proposals -
OL,8,Fdespite huge political objections - or
OL,9,Finsist on a sub-opt for the north. Even
OL,10,Fdoing this could still save jobs.
OL,12,FIt is important to remember that STV's
OL,13,Fcurrent service includes both Scottish
OL,14,Fnational news and stories of local and
OL,15,Fregional interest.
OL,17,FAll the news programmes in the nations
OL,18,Fare very different editorially to
OL,19,FEnglish regional programmes.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
