OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV currently has one advantage over
OL,7,Fthe BBC - it can also cover the kind of
OL,8,Flocal and regional stories which are
OL,9,Funlikely to be seen on Reporting
OL,10,FScotland.
OL,12,FBut is it fair to impose an obligation
OL,13,Fon a commercial broadcaster to do
OL,14,Fsomething which the BBC has never done?
OL,16,FThis is not 1961 or even 1993.
OL,18,FOr does the simple fact that ratings
OL,19,Ffor STV North are good mean that taking
OL,20,Fthe axe to the service is a huge
OL,21,Fmisjudgement?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
