OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV points out that it's legal
OL,7,Fobligations are greater than those of
OL,8,FUTV and ITV Wales.
OL,10,FAgainst this are two obvious points.
OL,11,FScotland is bigger than Wales or
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland and has always been
OL,13,Fsplit into three channel 3 regions.
OL,15,FAdd on changing consumer behaviour and
OL,16,Fyou can see that there is at least an
OL,17,Fargument - if not necessarily a
OL,18,Fcompelling case - for change.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
