OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,7,Fregions merely reflects transmitter
OL,8,Fareas. It is not as simple as saying
OL,9,FAberdeen is different to Glasgow.
OL,11,FIt is for all those reasons that Ofcom
OL,12,Fmay face big questions if it does not
OL,13,Frun a lengthy, detailed consultation.
OL,15,FUnions and politicians will be critical
OL,16,Fif Ofcom simply puts a proposed change
OL,17,Fof this magnitude out to a short
OL,18,Fconsultation.
